      "content": "I'm sorry you're feeling this way. It sounds like you're going through a really difficult time, and it's okay to feel empty or disconnected from who you used to be. Sometimes, when we go through significant changes or struggles, it can feel like we've lost our sense of self. If you're open to it, talking to a trusted friend or a mental health professional might help you navigate these feelings. You don't have to carry this alone.",
